summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3521 for the improvement of Sycamore Avenue, from West 60th Street to West 62nd Street; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 43600, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
